==English==
===Noun===
'''gonad''' (''plural:'' [[gonads]])

# {{anatomy}} A [[sex organ]] that produces [[gamete]]s; specifically, a [[testicle]] or [[ovary]].
#(''slang, used only in plural'' '''gonads''') The testicles.

